{"tid":1635263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要屌前線裝修？已經呼籲咗擺食擺買禁錢幾個月啦","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:53:30.000Z","uid":129812,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07eec83a8f9cbc865137821fd8567e9872c38571","tid":1635263,"uid":129812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"已經呼籲咗好耐，叫大家唔好食吉野家，結果呢？好多區晚市仲係滿座，仲要係有不少後生仔。<br />\n<br />\n前線有無屌你地和理非無做擺食擺買？有無屌文宣不力。對抗極權，我哋文宣，勇武，和理缺不割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n想前線停止裝修，麻煩大家&rdquo;的&rdquo;起心肝，擺買擺食無良藍店，做好文宣。如果杯葛有成效，前線就唔洗裝修。<br />\n<br />\n唯一要屌前線就係: 你哋做野唔該包實哂，一個口罩係無撚用㗎，唔好再露樣啦，好多鏡頭同cctv㗎，無嘢遮樣，麻煩你忍忍手。"},{"pid":"5e9be61dc22e51b83d176e6d930d375f2e705712","tid":1635263,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"叫翻班冷氣軍師兄弟爬山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3df1fa035a6c2420748a655687e0d8ca1028a0","tid":1635263,"uid":129812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuqUixV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuqUixV.png&h=45634f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋外國記者都叫我哋唔好屌前線啊"},{"pid":"f49b2c205b84efa01605910f5cc889b88628137d","tid":1635263,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnmPRT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnmPRT4.jpg&h=165f7a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c510b369a40b243912b6e4d7fd6f8eb66d3b74d","tid":1635263,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as